data.title: UEFA European Cup Matches 1991
data.meta_description: UEFA European Cup Football - UEFA European Cup Matches 1991/1992
data.text:
This page lists the matches of European club football in the season 1991/1992. These match results are input for the calculation of coefficients and rankings (menu at top of the page). See the database for an overview of all matches of European Cup football, or search in all matches since 1955.
